Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: Products.FakeZopeUser
Version: 1.0.1
Summary: A product that enables faking another logged-in user.
Home-page: http://www.nidelven-it.no/d
Author: Morten W. Petersen
Author-email: info@nidelven-it.no
License: GPL
Description: A simple product that enables overriding the logged-in (or default
        system/nobody user) and fake being a system user or some user stored
        in the database.
        
        Usable in a bare-bones Zope as well as within Zope add-ons.
        
        
        1.0.1 (2012-10-29)
        
          - Adding handler for faking Zope user outside of portal context,
            might be because of remember/membrane
        
        1.0 (2012-03-05)
        
          - Initial release
        
